OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FTurning cooler Thursday, with showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain by the afternoon.
OL,8,FLikely staying dry Friday with sunny
OL,9,Fspells, but increasingly breezy later.
OL,10,FRain into Saturday clearing to a
OL,11,Fbright day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
